{"tid":1156672,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去咗法國玩幾日，食完餐法國餐先發現無錢俾。。","createTime":"2019-05-15T18:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T03:35:57.000Z","uid":60393,"like":40,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"98c661fc7754b63b307d5ab875c31da5552c1034","tid":1156672,"uid":60393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:18:51.000Z","msg":"食完先發現自己身上無歐羅。。<br />\n銀包又得港幣英磅，同埋袋底d用剩既人仔係到。。<br />\n想問下佢收唔收港幣啦，點知又唔收。。<br />\n不過佢話英磅同人仔都收既。。<br />\n又話見我係華人，又咁慘咁，人生路不熟，用人仔有1折優惠喎。。<br />\n點做好。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：用人仔（還惦用剩係到 慳返d錢之後果幾日玩得開心d）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：用英磅（洗貴d都好 但d人仔咁臭 將d人仔掉落垃圾桶都唔會用）"},{"pid":"5379198cb7d274e60d9fc3398ce702bb8559c138","tid":1156672,"uid":27675,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:19:57.000Z","msg":"無錢走入人地餐廳做乜鳩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4d0e1f846fe4b221be1962c0c99be44c1ab4ad","tid":1156672,"uid":165598,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:21:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"451fc490d19f0a093509b9b7b9d029b3ad66d143","tid":1156672,"uid":63303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:21:42.000Z","msg":"留低洗碗"},{"pid":"088a5f9e5c80fadd8ee6db87ae8eac5644a14a14","tid":1156672,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:21:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國人擁有同使用人民幣係理所當然<br />\n中國香港人(達哥) 支持用簡體都係盡國民義務<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"1e8c1b8c707e6590ec51abdaffa17128b2214d25","tid":1156672,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T18:22:51.000Z","msg":"嫁個有錢人"},{"pid":"7f5f3ac6cb64aef0d3d2bc7ccb12536bcc6472ad","tid":1156672,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"088a5f9e5c80fadd8ee6db87ae8eac5644